name: Yesterday’s tadpoles #2
description:
Magic boo
We are a group of seven little frogs that have been making art for many many years, both together and separately. In the middle of the pandemic we started getting together every sunday to survive, and it became a ritual that continues today. In these meetings we draw, make and record music, give each other workshops, play ping pong and smoke magical herbs. Our way of working is collaborative, free and improvised: it does not matter who does what and we have no shame in covering, crossing out or stepping on what someone else did.
